BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (THE 3-DAY METHOD) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 684.0 Td (DAY 1: Introduction) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 666.0 Td (Morning: Say goodbye to diapers together \(throw away/donate\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 652.0 Td (Put child in underwear only \(no pants easier at first\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 638.0 Td (Every 15-20 minutes: 'Let's try sitting on the potty!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 624.0 Td (Watch for signs: squirming, holding, hiding, stopping play) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 610.0 Td (CELEBRATE every success - even just sitting!) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 596.0 Td (Accidents WILL happen. Stay calm: 'Oops! Pee goes in the potty.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.0 Td (Fluid loading: extra water/juice = more practice opportunities) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 552.2 Td (DAY 2: Building Awareness) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 534.2 Td (Extend time between reminders to 30 minutes) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 520.2 Td (Ask: 'Are your underwear dry? Let's keep them dry!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 506.2 Td (Child may start self-initiating today) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 492.2 Td (Fewer accidents expected but still normal) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 478.2 Td (Short outing \(30 min max\) with potty reminder before leaving) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 448.4 Td (DAY 3: Independence) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 430.4 Td (Let child take the lead - remind less often) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 416.4 Td (Longer outing with portable potty or planned bathroom stops) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 402.4 Td (Practice pants up and down independently) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 388.4 Td (Handwashing routine established) Tj ET
endstream
