BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (TROUBLESHOOTING COMMON ISSUES) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 686.0 Td (Refuses to sit on potty:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 670.0 Td (- Don't force! Let them sit with clothes on first) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.0 Td (- Try during a preferred activity \(tablet, book\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.0 Td (- Make it fun - sing songs, blow bubbles while sitting) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 624.0 Td (Pees fine but won't poop on potty:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 608.0 Td (- This is VERY common - poop takes longer to master) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 594.0 Td (- Offer a diaper for poop if needed \(then gradually transition\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 580.0 Td (- Ensure feet are supported \(stool\) for proper positioning) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 562.0 Td (Regression after weeks of success:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 546.0 Td (- Check for: new sibling, move, stress, illness) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 532.0 Td (- Go back to more frequent reminders temporarily) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 518.0 Td (- NEVER shame or punish - it makes it worse) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 500.0 Td (Nighttime dryness:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 484.0 Td (- Separate from daytime - can take months to years longer) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 470.0 Td (- Use waterproof mattress cover and pull-ups at night) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 456.0 Td (- Limit fluids 1 hour before bed) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 442.0 Td (- Not developmental until age 5-6 for many children) Tj ET
